Download guard, sorting repos... bunch of other stuff.

Filtered out temporary emails, make sure to pull disposable-email-domains repo
Fixed registration unique errors handling, suppressed diesel warnings, changed helper to self to work around intellij rust errors, removed unused imports, fixed register_submit links
